---
title: Chicken Sausage & Mushroom Flatbreads with Caramelized Onion & Balsamic Arugula Salad
description: Crispy flatbreads topped with melty mozzarella, jammy caramelized onion, cream cheese, and savory sautéed mushrooms make for a quick and easy meal that’s perfect any time of day. A bright, peppery arugula salad tossed with creamy, tangy balsamic dressing adds fresh balance and pop of vibrant color—all in a speedy 25 minutes!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/685bf6ef559308f509950d3a-84deb354.jpeg
